      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This specimen is mechanically flawless, having undergone a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a proactive rod bearing replacement with VAC coated bearings and ARP bolts. The chassis integrity is verified with a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the platform's primary weak point. Performance is optimized via the factory M-Variable Differential Lock and a perfectly tuned suspension featuring fresh bushings throughout. The exterior retains its original depth and luster, while the interior showcases immaculate Nappa leather with zero bolster compression. This is a collector-grade example for the purist who demands peak mechanical synchronization and aesthetic perfection.",
