      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true time-capsule vehicle that has been meticulously preserved since day one. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating, the exterior is free of swirls, rock chips, or door dings. Every panel gap is factory-perfect. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dashboard is free of any UV fading, and it still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships, with every fluid flush and inspection performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage shows no signs of salt or inclement weather exposure. Always garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in the rain, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a comprehensive binder of service documentation.",
